# Exclude unnecessary C++ files from GitHub's language statistics
*.cpp linguist-ignore-as-documentation
*.h linguist-ignore-as-documentation
*.hpp linguist-ignore-as-documentation
*.cxx linguist-ignore-as-documentation
*.cc linguist-ignore-as-documentation

# If there are specific C++ files that were accidentally included, you can also exclude entire directories
**/build/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation
**/windows/runner/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation
**/android/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation
**/ios/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation
**/macos/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation
**/linux/** linguist-ignore-as-documentation

# Explicitly mark Dart files as the primary language for this Flutter project
*.dart linguist-detectable=true